:"A^uHoSina","text_ar":"اُحْصِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"be not allowable as meaning, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoSana","text_ar":"اَحْصَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", “ he married, ” or “ took a wife: ” but see 1 and 4]. (S, Msb.) For the fem.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHoSanapN","text_ar":"مُحْصَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHoSanaAtN","text_ar":"مُحْصَنَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSaAnN","text_ar":"حَصَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":["Zj","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}